  "title": "Aurelius, Meditations §aur_07_xxviii: He hath a stronger body, and is a better wrestler than I.",
  "body": "He hath a stronger body, and is a better wrestler than I. What then? Is he more bountiful? is he more modest? Doth he bear all adverse chances with more equanimity: or with his neighbour's offences with more meekness and gentleness than I?",
